Valuable Email DKIM/DMARC learning Material

If an email fails to send or be recieved. This is another way of finding a solution to the problem.

Powershell Commands:

nslookup

server

set type=TXT
_DMARC.domain.domain

_DMARC.domain.domain for examples


 v=DMARC1;p=none;sp=none;adkim=r;aspf=r;pct=100;fo=0;rf=afrf;ri=86400 (Strict mode)

Name; _DMARC.FNS.co.uk
Type; TXT
Value; v=DMARC1; p=none; pct=50; ruf=mailto:dmarc@FNS.co.uk; rua=mailto:dmarc@FNS.co.uk; adkim=r; aspf=r (Relaxed (Learning Mode))
